snippet.title: Pikmin RPG - OFFICIAL REVEAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
This is the Pikmin RPG! This is a turn based, completely hand drawn Pikmin fan game that is now in development! (This is in no way affiliated with Nintendo, it is all fan made!)

Make sure to join the Pikmin RPG's Discord server, for a super active and chill chat, weekly contests, RPG updates, and more! https://discord.gg/JedGeQrT29

And here is the Pikmin RPG's twitter! https://twitter.com/PikminRpg

Trailer art by Jason Lupas.

#Pikmin #PikminRPG #Nintendo

Click here to subscribe! ▶ https://www.youtube.com/user/megabbones
